  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in the ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add cumin seeds and coriander seeds and toast until fragrant.",
    "Add chopped onion and bell pepper and sauté until softened.",
    "Add chopped ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add soaked blackeye peas, smoked paprika, crushed red pepper, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add lemon juice and pour in enough water to cover the peas.",
    "Bring to a boil, then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 45 minutes.",
    "Stir occasionally and add more water as needed.",
    "After 45 minutes, check for tenderness and adjust seasoning if needed.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped fresh herbs or lemon wedges."
  ],
